                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is no documentation in the &lt;tt&gt;lfs-changelog.1&lt;/tt&gt; man page or in the Lustre Manual about what the fields printed by &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs changelog&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; actually mean.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
